{"descriptions":[{"id":1358,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eTibetan has several expressions that mean \u0026ldquo;why\u0026rdquo;: \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་རེ་ཡིན་ན་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་རེ་བྱས་ནས་\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཁོང་ཞེད་ཀྱི་འདུག\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་རེ་ཡིན་ན།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;He\u0026rsquo;s afraid\u0026mdash;why?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eང་རྐང་པ་ན་གིས།\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་རེ་ཡིན་ན།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;My leg\u0026rsquo;s hurting\u0026mdash;(I wonder) why?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་རེ་བྱས་ནས་ངུ་གི་ཡོད།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Why are you crying?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eག་རེ་བྱས་ནས་རྡོ་ཞུས་པ།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Why did you throw stones?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eAnother formulation for asking \u0026ldquo;why\u0026rdquo; can be constructed like this:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eVerb + \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eནས་ག་རེ་བྱེད་ག\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eVerb + \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབྱས་ག་རེ་བྱེད་ག\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThese may be translated as \u0026ldquo;What do you mean by + \u003cem\u003egerundive\u003c/em\u003e.\u0026rdquo; This construction often figures in reproaches:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eདཀར་ཡོལ་བཅག་ནས་ཀ་རེ་བྱེད་ག\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Why did you break the cup?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརྡོ་ཞུས་ནས་ཀ་རེ་བྱེད་ག\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Why did you throw stones?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eལས་ཀ་མ་བྱས་པ་བྱས་ཀ་རེ་བྱེད་ག\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Why didn\u0026rsquo;t you do any work?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:43 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:43 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}